Package: RCMap
Type: Package
Title: Group Concept Mapping
Version: 0.3.0
Author: Haim Bar
Maintainer: Haim Bar <haim.bar@uconn.edu>
Description: An open-source implementation of group concept mapping in R.
    Provides a menu-driven interface (RCMapMenu()) for the full concept mapping
    workflow: pile-sort data ingestion with fuzzy label standardisation,
    multidimensional scaling, hierarchical clustering, Jaccard-index stability
    analysis, split-half reliability, misplacement-index visualisation, and
    cohort-based rating plots and reports. All tunable parameters are exposed
    through an automatically generated project configuration file (config.txt).
